 <div class="new-our-store">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="new-our-store__wrap">
          <div class="left">
            <div class="left__wrap">
              <div class="subtitle-2">
                <p>
                  {{section.settings.name}}
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="title">
                <h3>
                  {{section.settings.title}}
                </h3>
              </div>
              <div class="text-1">
                {{section.settings.text}}
              </div>
              <div class="new-our-btn">
                <a href="{{ sectin.settings.url }}" class="new-a-btn"> {{ section.settings.btn_name}}</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="right">
            <div class="rigth__wrap">
              <div class="image">
                <img src="{{section.settings.img | img_url: 'master'}}" alt="" width="" height="">
              </div>
              <div class="subtitle-1">
                <p>
                  {{section.settings.author}}
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="subtitle">
                <p>
                  {{section.settings.author_subtitle}}
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
     </div>



{% schema %}
    {
      "name": "new-our-store",
      "settings": [
         {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "name",
          "label": "name",
          "default":"our story"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "title",
          "label": "title",
          "default":"Result of dedication and passion for natural hair care"
        },
        {
          "type": "richtext",
          "id": "text",
          "label": "text",
          "default":"<p>My momâ€™s dressing table was adorned with thick waxy lipsticks, rich creams in pots, and heavy scents in glass jars, creating a picture of glamour and elegance that has remained my inspiration. I never gave up on my love for cosmetics and desire for radiant hair.</p> <p> Later in life, I created my own natural products free of harmful substances, which led to healthy, strong, and shiny hair. I wanted to share my invention with others which led me to over 2 years of clinical research in cooperation with the best cosmetic laboratories in Switzerland.</p> <p> Over many years, applying their expertise with advanced techniques, our unique products were created, blending tradition with innovation.</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "btn_name",
          "label": "btn name",
          "default":"Read our Story"
        },
        {
          "type": "url",
          "id": "url",
          "label": "btn url"
        }, {
          "type": "image_picker",
          "id": "img",
          "label": "image"
        },{
          "type": "text",
          "id": "author",
          "label": "author",
          "default":"Sarah-Jane Bayliss"
        },{
          "type": "text",
          "id": "author_subtitle",
          "label": "author subtitle",
          "default":"LEDA SWISS FOuNDER"
        }
      ],
      "presets": [
        {   
          "name": "new-our-store"
        }
      ]
    }
  {% endschema %}